{
  "stem": "17625.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 177.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Cracow, I-- I-- I continued to do what I did at home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But also, I tried to be involved in business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whatever my father did at home-- we had like representation from-- from-- from a, from a firm, from a manufacturer, and I went around to sell.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I did quite well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Started up, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, that my, my brother followed me from Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I made customers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had a representation from, from, from a, a manufacturer, a big-- a good manufacturer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we opened up in Cracow then a-- also a shop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I was also [SIGH] busy in the same-- the same way I did at home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I joined people there by learning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's how I spent the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Radomsk shtibl.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the main [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were about 15.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it as, it was a few shtibls-- from Radomsk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, I'm talking about-- there were a lot of shtibls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But every-- there was a lot of Hasidic shtibls So mine was Radomsk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I learned there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived in Cracow on the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The number-- I don't remember the number.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went with-- I lived there with-- with a guy by a-- by a family named [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave me space.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I lived there with a friend, also, also from Chrzanow, which also departed to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't want to go to the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was his name, from Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we lived together there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We rented a whatever-- a bed, a room, not apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What did I say was his name?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] or [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where I lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father came to Cracow, also, on business.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
